{"tid":1624832,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非/前線適用] 中資 / 賣港商舖? 唔洗裝修架","createTime":"2019-10-05T04:59:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T05:36:01.000Z","uid":197256,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d8f963c6af496ca37a2421a6432c08cf1a4e6de8","tid":1624832,"uid":197256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:59:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">瘋狂貼文宣咪得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地誓要將佢地進化成 <span style=\"color: red;\">【連儂舖】</span><br />\n<br />\n以往我地只會喺佢閘外貼野宣傳<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eYXOOOh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeYXOOOh.jpg&h=c18c822b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6hpBdeX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6hpBdeX.jpg&h=b00f1ba1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家我地喺閘內, 舖頭內, 佢撕一, 我貼千,<br />\n貼撚到佢驚, 貼撚到佢拉閘<br />\n<br />\n咁就裝修功夫都慳番 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n佢拉左閘又賺唔到錢, 符合制裁目的<br />\n<br />\n所以各位, 呢個絕對係和理非加前線一齊做既合作活動<br />\n揀番自己區玩就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n認同既幫手推下<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"6e8df138e130240c0ecf3e5c3aff5d116f83e6ee","tid":1624832,"uid":197256,"l